name: Yonatan Bentzur
description: Yonatan is originally from Israel and moved to the Bay Area about 4 years ago. After completing his BSc in Computer Sceince from one of the leading universities in Israel he started working at Wix.com, the Israeli website builder, as a frontend (web) engineer. After moving to the US he started working at a small startup called Lustre.ai (formerly Slant.co) and he's been there for the past 3.5 years.

name: Lauren Wong
description: Lauren is an 11th Grader at the Nueva School in San Mateo. She started coding in 3rd grade and is the founder of the STEMinism Club at her school and the CS4Girls summer program. She is also the developer of the app DoNation for iOS and the web.
